snippet.title: 10 Miles To Safety - Fast Paced Zombie Survival Crafting Roguelite
snippet.description:
10 Miles to Safety Gameplay with Splat! Let's Play 10 Miles to Safety and check out a game where you'll run the distance of a city in order to achieve safety through crafting, building, and finding new weapons!

Download 10 Miles to Safety : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1015140/10_Miles_To_Safety/
